OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1776819790
OL,3,CHospital cuts carbon emissions through
OL,4,Ctheatre upgrade
OL,6,FUniversity Hospital Southampton has
OL,7,Fsignificantly reduced its carbon
OL,8,Femissions through a major upgrade to
OL,9,Fits operating theatres.
OL,11,FImprovements to the pipework in
OL,12,Ftheatres has significantly reduced
OL,13,Fwaste from anaesthetic gases,
OL,14,Fprimarily by cutting nitrous oxide use.
OL,16,FNitrous oxide, known as laughing gas
OL,17,Fis used as part of anaesthetic care
OL,18,Fduring some surgeries as well as for
OL,19,Fpain relief.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
