OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1776819790
OL,3,CHospital cuts carbon emissions through
OL,4,Ctheatre upgrade
OL,6,FBut according to health bosses
OL,7,Fanaesthetic gases account for around
OL,8,F5% of global healthcare emissions,
OL,9,Fwith nitrous oxide a significant
OL,10,Fcontributor due to its high heat
OL,11,Ftrapping effect and its long lifetime
OL,12,Fin the atmosphere.
OL,14,FIt is also a major greenhouse gas and
OL,15,Fthe primary contributor to ozone layer
OL,16,Fdestruction.JThe work is part of the
OL,17,FNHS ambition toachievenet zero
OL,18,Femissionsby 2040.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
