OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1776819790
OL,3,CHospital cuts carbon emissions through
OL,4,Ctheatre upgrade
OL,6,FAndy Fox,deputychiefpharmacist at
OL,7,FUHS andproject lead, said:"By
OL,8,Fswitching off an outdated system that
OL,9,Fwas leaking gas around the clock,
OL,10,Fwe'vedelivered a major carbon saving
OL,11,Fwithout compromising patient care.
OL,13,F"Cutting nitrous oxide leakage by 87
OL,14,Fper cent is a significant step forward
OL,15,Ffor sustainability at UHS and shows
OL,16,Fhow modernising hospital
OL,17,Finfrastructure can make a real
OL,18,Fdifference.
OL,26,@oD@]OUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/5
