CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1776819790
OL,3,CHospital cuts carbon emissions through
OL,4,Ctheatre upgrade
OL,6,F"The change has also delivered cost
OL,7,Fsavings for the Trust and improved
OL,8,Fstaff safety by reducing occupational
OL,9,Fexposure to nitrous oxide.
OL,11,F"This was a complex piece of work and
OL,12,Fvery much a team effort.
OL,14,F"It would not have been possible
OL,15,Fwithout the commitment and
OL,16,Fcollaboration of colleagues from
OL,17,Fpharmacy, anaesthetics, clinical
OL,18,Fengineering, portering,estatesand
OL,19,Ffinance."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOU{D@IO]
